  "general_conditions": "Cargo dues are levied at all ports to recover cargo contribution towards port infrastructure. The unit of tonnage is 1 metric ton (1000 kg), subject to a minimum of 1 ton.  All packaging is included.  Tonnage must be substantiated by documentation. Late order fees apply for incorrectly declared tonnage. Minimum fee for breakbulk is based on 1 ton.",
